name: Momotaro
ability: Moderately increases DMG dealt by Divina team members when this daemon is Team Leader.

additional_data.description: The legendary demon-fighting warrior accompanied by a dog, monkey and pheasant. He wasn't the best in terms of swordsmanship or other fighting abilities, but his innate bravery, endless care for his friends, and visionary leadership enabled him to achieve his goals. Now, after much, much training and practice he has finally managed to become a top-class fighter.
additional_data.how_to_acquire:
◦ Obtained after clearing Chapter 8.
◦ Available in Jewel Summon after clearing Chapter 8.

main: "Gather, comrades. There is someone we must defeat!"
summon: "I don't see dreams -- I seize dreams."
limit_break: "I've always had the potential for this..."
